The article is a fact sheet on immigration issued on April 5, 2019. It states that the current situation at the southern border is seen as a border security and humanitarian crisis that poses a threat to national security. President Donald J. Trump has repeatedly warned that the border is being overwhelmed, and the numbers support this claim. The President is taking action within his lawful authority to secure the border and respond to the crisis. The article also emphasizes the need for Congress to act immediately to fix the broken immigration system and address the root causes of the crisis at the border.